title: Hour 1: Dabo in the House!
description:
Chris Russo, Jay Williams, and Ryan Clark debate on whether Davante Adams will regret leaving Aaron Rodgers. The guys talk about who the best team in AFC West is and which team from the division is most likely to miss the playoffs. Clemson's Dabo Swinney stops by to discuss the upcoming CFB season.
